# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Netz Analysis Engine — Cloudflare Environment Template
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# This file lists ALL secrets/vars needed across Cloudflare services.
# Copy values to Cloudflare Dashboard (DO NOT commit filled values).
#
# Usage:
#   1. Fill in values below
#   2. Use `wrangler secret put <NAME>` or paste in Cloudflare Dashboard
#   3. Delete this file after provisioning (or keep empty as reference)
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Shared across ALL containers and workers ──────────────────────

# Generated token — same value in: netz-backend, netz-workers, netz-gateway, netz-cron
WORKER_DISPATCH_SECRET=Gwq3H8bEhDqOCVIks8Xd4dJZugKTrl_KlfX54jYyi7c

# ── Database (Timescale Cloud) ────────────────────────────────────
# Where: netz-backend, netz-workers
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://tsdbadmin:<PASSWORD>@<HOST>:30124/tsdb?ssl=true

# ── Redis (Upstash) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Where: netz-backend, netz-workers
REDIS_URL=rediss://default:<PASSWORD>@<HOST>.upstash.io:6379

# ── AI Providers ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Where: netz-backend, netz-workers
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
MISTRAL_API_KEY=...

# ── Auth (Clerk) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Where: netz-backend, netz-workers
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_live_...
CLERK_JWKS_URL=https://<clerk-domain>/.well-known/jwks.json

# ── Storage (Cloudflare R2 — S3-compatible) ──────────────────────
# Where: netz-backend, netz-workers
FEATURE_R2_ENABLED=true
R2_ACCOUNT_ID=a44ddf3ff0612bc0f62d1ee86f465ac9
R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID=...
R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=...
R2_BUCKET_NAME=netz-data-lake

# ── App Config ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Where: netz-backend, netz-workers (set as vars, not secrets)
APP_ENV=production

# ── SEC EDGAR ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Where: netz-backend, netz-workers (public identifier, not a secret)
EDGAR_IDENTITY=Netz Analysis Engine tech@netzco.com

# ── FRED API ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Where: netz-workers (macro ingestion worker)
FRED_API_KEY=...


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Gateway Worker (netz-gateway)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Set in: Dashboard → Workers → netz-gateway → Settings

# Secret:
# WORKER_SECRET = <same as WORKER_DISPATCH_SECRET above>

# Var:
# BACKEND_ORIGIN = https://netz-backend.<account>.containers.cloudflare.com


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Cron Worker (netz-cron)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Set in: Dashboard → Workers → netz-cron → Settings

# Secret:
# WORKER_SECRET = <same as WORKER_DISPATCH_SECRET above>

# Var:
# WORKERS_ORIGIN = https://netz-workers.<account>.containers.cloudflare.com


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Cloudflare Pages — Frontend Apps
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Set in: Dashboard → Pages → <project> → Settings → Environment Variables

# ── netz-credit ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL = https://api.netz.app
# PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY = pk_live_...

# ── netz-wealth ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL = https://api.netz.app
# PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY = pk_live_...

# ── netz-admin ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL = https://api.netz.app
# PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY = pk_live_...


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GitHub Actions Secrets
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Set in: GitHub → Settings → Secrets → Actions

# CF_API_TOKEN = <Cloudflare API token with Workers + Containers + R2 permissions>
# CF_ACCOUNT_ID = a44ddf3ff0612bc0f62d1ee86f465ac9


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DNS Records (Cloudflare DNS)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# api.netz.app      → CNAME → netz-gateway.<account>.workers.dev (proxied)
# credit.netz.app   → Pages custom domain (auto-configured)
# wealth.netz.app   → Pages custom domain (auto-configured)
# admin.netz.app    → Pages custom domain (auto-configured)


# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# wrangler secret put — Quick Reference
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Backend container:
#   cd infra/cloudflare
#   wrangler secret put DATABASE_URL --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put REDIS_URL --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put OPENAI_API_KEY --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put MISTRAL_API_KEY --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put CLERK_SECRET_KEY --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put CLERK_JWKS_URL --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put WORKER_DISPATCH_SECRET --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put FRED_API_KEY --config wrangler.backend.jsonc
#
# Workers container (same secrets):
#   wrangler secret put DATABASE_URL --config wrangler.workers.jsonc
#   wrangler secret put REDIS_URL --config wrangler.workers.jsonc
#   ... (repeat all above with --config wrangler.workers.jsonc)
#
# Gateway worker:
#   cd infra/cloudflare/gateway
#   wrangler secret put WORKER_SECRET
#
# Cron worker:
#   cd infra/cloudflare/cron
#   wrangler secret put WORKER_SECRET
